":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：BBS means Bulletin Board Service. （BBS的意思是电子公告板"},{"type":"text","text":"系统。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Oh, I see, but what's it used for? （哦，我明白了。但它是用来"},{"type":"text","text":"干什么的？）"}]}]}